        "description": {
          "TYPE": "Text",
          "NULLABLE": false,
          "UNIQUE": null,
          "DEFAULT": null,
          "CHECKS": [],
          "IS_PRIMARY": false,
          "IS_INDEX": false,
          "VALUES": [
            "<ul>\r\n\t<li>Specification:</li>\r\n\t<li>Name: BLON BL-03</li>\r\n\t<li>Earphone&nbsp;type:&nbsp;In-ear</li>\r\n\t<li>Driver unit:&nbsp;10mm Carbon Diaphragm Dynamic Drive</li>\r\n\t<li>Impedance: 32&Omega;</li>\r\n\t<li>Earphone&nbsp;sensitivity:&nbsp;102dB/mW</li>\r\n\t<li>Frequency range: 20-20000Hz</li>\r\n\t<li>Interface: 3.5mm&nbsp;Gilded</li>\r\n\t<li>Plug Type: L curved</li>\r\n\t<li>Cable Length:&nbsp;1.2m&plusmn;3cm</li>\r\n\t<li>Interface:&nbsp;2Pin 0.78MM&nbsp;&nbsp;connector</li>\r\n\t<li>Microphone:&nbsp;Yes</li>\r\n\t<li>Detachable Cable: Yes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
            "<PERSON>",
            "<ul>\r\n\t<li>Brand Etymotic Research</li>\r\n\t<li>Connections = wired</li>\r\n\t<li>Model Name ETYER2SE</li>\r\n\t<li>Color Multicolored</li>\r\n\t<li>Headphones Form Factor In Ear</li>\r\n\t<li>About this item</li>\r\n\t<li>True high-accuracy sound experience</li>\r\n\t<li>Metal earpieces with anodized ?nish</li>\r\n\t<li>35+ dB of external noise isolation</li>\r\n\t<li>Assortment of ear tips for the perfect in-ear ?t</li>\r\n\t<li>Detachable cable allows for easy replacement</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Detachable, 4-foot cable</li>\r\n\t<li>Foam and 3-flange ear tips</li>\r\n\t<li>Filter removal tool and filters</li>\r\n\t<li>Compact storage pouch</li>\r\n\t<li>Shirt clip</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
            "<ul>\r\n\t<li>Product Name : NICEHCK Traceless earbud</li>\r\n\t<li>Brand : NICEHCK</li>\r\n\t<li>Model : Traceless</li>\r\n\t<li>Type : Earbud</li>\r\n\t<li>Impedance : 32&Omega;</li>\r\n\t<li>Earphone sensitivity : 115dB/mW</li>\r\n\t<li>Frequency range : 20-20000Hz</li>\r\n\t<li>Earphone plug type : 3.5mm straight plug</li>\r\n\t<li>Cable Length : 1.2m&plusmn;5cm</li>\r\n\t<li>Whether with Mic : With Mic / No Mic ( two versions can choose)</li>\r\n\t<li>Driver unit : Single 15.4mm PET Dynamic Drive unit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
            "<p>Spesifikasi :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Sound Pressur Level : 112dB</li>\r\n\t<li>Frequency response: 20Hz-20kHz</li>\r\n\t<li>Connector type : straight</li>\r\n\t<li>Impedance: 32ohm</li>\r\n\t<li>Maximum input power: 1mW</li>\r\n\t<li>Cable length: 1.3m</li>\r\n\t<li>Plug: 3.5mm stereo straight plug</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
            "<ul>\r\n\t<li>Dual ES9118</li>\r\n\t<li>Dual crystal oscillators</li>\r\n\t<li>3.5mm SE + 2.5mm balanced</li>\r\n\t<li>Native DSD128</li>\r\n\t<li>USB mode switch, 1.0 dan 2.0</li>\r\n\t<li>Aluminum alloy body</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
            "<ul>\r\n\t<li>Dimensions 72&times;32&times;11.1mm</li>\r\n\t<li>Bluetooth 5.0 Supported Audio Format(s) AAC/SBC/aptX/aptX LL/ aptX HD/LDAC</li>\r\n\t<li>NFC Supported</li>\r\n\t<li>Mic Function Support Bluetooth call,</li>\r\n\t<li>built-in omnidirectional microphone;</li>\r\n\t<li>support external microphone of CTIA cable</li>\r\n\t<li>Headphone Output</li>\r\n\t<li>3.5 mm stereo jack</li>\r\n\t<li>USB Port</li>\r\n\t<li>Type C USB</li>\r\n\t<li>Balanced Headphone Output 2.5mm jack Drive Ability 16~100&Omega;?PO?</li>\r\n\t<li>16~150&Omega;?BAL?</li>\r\n\t<li>Channel Balance &le;0.1 dB Gain Supported(High/Low)</li>\r\n\t<li>Volume Control Side buttons Status indication The display indicates the Bluetooth code,</li>\r\n\t<li>charging, battery, volume, sampling rate, menu</li>\r\n\t<li>APP interconnection Supports setting through App Bluetooth Codes Display Supported</li>\r\n\t<li>Charging Time &le;1.5 h (DC 5V 500mA) Power Input Recommend DC 5V 500mA</li>\r\n\t<li>Battery Capacity 550 mAh</li>\r\n\t<li>Output Power</li>\r\n\t<li>PO about 80mW?32&Omega; loaded? Frequency Response 20Hz?20kHz (aptX connection?</li>\r\n\t<li>PO about 90mW?16&Omega; loaded?</li>\r\n\t<li>BAL about 240mW?32&Omega; loaded? 20Hz?40kHz (LDAC connection?</li>\r\n\t<li>BAL about 240mW?16&Omega; loaded?</li>\r\n\t<li>THD+N PO?0.003%(LDAC 1kHz A-weighted) Output Impedance PO&le;1.0&Omega;?32&Omega; loaded?</li>\r\n\t<li>BAL?0.002%(LDAC 1kHz A-weighted) BAL&le;2.0&Omega;?32&Omega; loaded?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
            "<LOCATION>",
            "<ul>\r\n\t<li>SIM Single SIM (Nano-SIM) or Hybrid Dual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)</li>\r\n\t<li>Size 6.5 inches, 101.0 cm2 (~84.8% screen-to-body ratio)</li>\r\n\t<li>PLATFORM OS Android 10, One UI 2.5</li>\r\n\t<li>Chipset Exynos 990 (7 nm+)</li>\r\n\t<li>CPU Octa-core (2x2.73 GHz Mongoose M5 &amp; 2x2.50 GHz Cortex-A76 &amp; 4x2.0 GHz Cortex-A55)</li>\r\n\t<li>GPU Mali-G77 MP11</li>\r\n\t<li>MEMORY Card slot microSDXC (uses shared SIM slot)</li>\r\n\t<li>Internal 128GB 8GB RAM,</li>\r\n\t<li>MAIN CAMERA Triple 12 MP,</li>\r\n\t<li>8 MP,</li>\r\n\t<li>12 MP,</li>\r\n\t<li>SELFIE CAMERA Single 32 MP,</li>\r\n\t<li>BATTERY Type Li-Po 4500 mAh, non-removable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
            "<LOCATION>",
            "<ul>\r\n\t<li>Display: 12.9&nbsp;inches (2160 x 1620 pixels)</li>\r\n\t<li>Storage: 128GB</li>\r\n\t<li>CPU: A12 Bionic</li>\r\n\t<li>Camera: 8MP</li>\r\n\t<li>Video recording: 1080p at 30 fps</li>\r\n\t<li>Front camera: 1.2MP</li>\r\n\t<li>Battery life (claimed): Up to 9 hours</li>\r\n\t<li>Size: 9.8 x 6.8 x 0.29 inches</li>\r\n\t<li>Weight: 1.08 pounds</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
            "<PERSON>",
            "<p>PowerLine Select+ [A8032] USB-C to USB-C 2.0 Cable for Samsung, Oppo, Xiaomi, Realmi, Vivo, etc<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*Length : 3 feet / 0,9m<br />\r\n*Double braided nylon<br />\r\n*Connector One: Type-C | Connector Two: Type-C<br />\r\n*Cable Speed: 480 Mbps<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWarna: Hitam<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSangat Tahan Lama: Pengisian Daya dan Kabel Data Double Braided Nylon.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPengiriman Daya: Mendukung Pengiriman Daya Pengisian Berkecepatan Tinggi untuk Ponsel, Tablet, dan Laptop.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDibangun Kuat: Ujung konektor yang diperkuat dan kabel nilon yang dikepang dapat menahan 15.000 Tekukan</p>\r\n",
            "<ul>\r\n\t<li>Processor: AMD Ryzen&trade; 9 5900HS Processor 3.1 GHz (16M Cache, up to 4.5 GHz)</li>\r\n\t<li>Memory: 8GB DDR4 on board + 8GB DDR4-3200 SO-DIMM</li>\r\n\t<li>Storage: 1TB M.2 NVMe&trade; PCIe&reg; 3.0 SSD</li>\r\n\t<li>Grafis : NVIDIA&reg; GeForce RTX&trade; 3060 Laptop GPU</li>\r\n\t<li>With ROG Boost up to 1525MHz at 80W (95W with Dynamic Boost)</li>\r\n\t<li>6GB GDDR6</li>\r\n\t<li>Display: 15.6-inch QHD (2560 x 1440) 16:9 300nits anti-glare IPS-levelPantone validated panel</li>\r\n\t<li>Operating System: Windows 10 Home</li>\r\n\t<li>Bundled Software : Office Home Student 2019</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
            "<p>Specification :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Graphics : NVIDIA GeForce&reg; RTX 3060, 6GB GDDR6</li>\r\n\t<li>Processor Onboard : Intel&reg; Core&trade; i5-10200H Processor (8M Cache, up to 4.10 GHz)</li>\r\n\t<li>Memory : 16 GB DDR4 3200Mhz (8*2)</li>\r\n\t<li>Display : 15.6&quot; FHD (1920*1080), IPS-Level 144Hz Thin Bezel</li>\r\n\t<li>Storage : 512GB NVMe PCIe Gen3x4 SSD</li>\r\n\t<li>Chipset : Intel HM470</li>\r\n\t<li>Keyboard : Single Red Keyboard</li>\r\n\t<li>Camera : HD type (30fps@720p)</li>\r\n\t<li>Wireless Network : Intel Wi-Fi 6 AX201(2*2 ax) + BlueTooth 5.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nInterfaces :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>1x RJ45</li>\r\n\t<li>1x (4K @ 30Hz) HDMI</li>\r\n\t<li>1x Type-C USB3.2 Gen1</li>\r\n\t<li>3x Type-A USB3.2 Gen1</li>\r\n\t<li>1x M.2 SSD Combo slot (NVMe PCIe Gen3 / SATA</li>\r\n\t<li>Operating System : Windows 10 Home</li>\r\n\t<li>Batteray : 3 cell , 51Whr</li>\r\n\t<li>Dimension : 359 x 254 x 21.7 mm</li>\r\n\t<li>Weight: 1,86Kg</li>\r\n\t<li>Adapter : 120W adapter</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
            "<PERSON>",
            "<PHONE_NUMBER>",
            "<p>SPECIFICATION</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Number of Keys: 84 keys</li>\r\n\t<li>Layout: ANSI</li>\r\n\t<li>Version: Gateron / Optical Hot-swappable</li>\r\n\t<li>Switches: Low profile Gateron mechanical / Low profile Keychron Optical</li>\r\n\t<li>Number of Multimedia Keys: 12</li>\r\n\t<li>Frame Material: ABS+Aluminum frame</li>\r\n\t<li>Keycap Material: ABS</li>\r\n\t<li>Example compatible keycaps: Roccat Vulcan 120 Aimo, Cooler Master SK630/SK631/SK650/SK651, Corsair K70 RGB MK.2, Alienware AW510K</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nCONNECTIVITY AND POWER</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Backlit Types: 18</li>\r\n\t<li>Backlit: Adjustable 4-level RGB backlit</li>\r\n\t<li>System: Windows/Android/Mac/iOS</li>\r\n\t<li>Battery: 1550mAh Rechargeable li-polymer battery</li>\r\n\t<li>BT Working Time (Single LED): Up to 34 hours (Lab test result may vary by actual use)</li>\r\n\t<li>BT Working Time (RGB): Up to 34 hours (Lab test result may vary by actual use)</li>\r\n\t<li>Connection: Bluetooth and Type-C cable</li>\r\n\t<li>Bluetooth version: 5.1</li>\r\n\t<li>Bluetooth Device Name: Keychron K3</li>\r\n\t<li>Compatible System: macOS/Windows</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
