            "<LOCATION>",
            "<p>Spesifikasi Canon PIXMA MG2570S</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>PRINT</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Speed 8.0 ipm (Black) - 4.0 ipm (Color)<br />\r\nResolution 4800 x 600 dpi<br />\r\nInk Droplet 2 pl (min.)<br />\r\nPaper Size A4, A5, B5, LTR, LGL, 4 x 6&quot;, 5 x 7&quot;, Envelopes (DL, COM10), Custum size (width 101.6mm - 215.9mm, length 152.4mm - 676mm)<br />\r\nCartridge Type PG-745S, CL-746S (PG-745, CL-746,PG-745XL,C;-746XL - optional)</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>SCAN</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Type Flatbed<br />\r\nScanning Method CIS (Contact Image Sensor)<br />\r\nResolution 600 x 1200 dpi<br />\r\nScanning Speed / Line Gray scale : 1.2 ms/line (300dpi)<br />\r\nColour : 3.5 ms/line (300dpi)<br />\r\nScan Bit Depth (In/Out) Gray Scale : 16/8 bits<br />\r\nColour : 48 / 24 bits (RGB 16 bits / 8 bits )</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>COPY</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Speed Colour : (A4 / Plain Paper / Max Speed ) : 1.6 ipm<br />\r\nImage Quality 2 positions (Fast &amp; Standart)<br />\r\nNumber of Copies 1 - 21 Pages<br />\r\nCompatible Media A4 &amp; LTR</p>\r\n",
            "<LOCATION>",
            "<p>Fitur :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>- Eartip core has a inner diameter of 4.5 mm</li>\r\n\t<li>- Included in the box for the high-end earphone AKG N5005</li>\r\n\t<li>- Ergonomically designed with the ability to flex in all direction and conform to the ear canal</li>\r\n\t<li>- Perfect for those hard to fit ears, and earphones with awkward insertion angles</li>\r\n\t<li>- Premium soft silicone material provides great comfort and durability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n"
